defs.name: midi_to_freq
defs.docs: Converts a midi note to frequency

attributes.value: / Converts a midi note to frequency
/ A midi note is an integer, generally in the range of 21 to 108

defs.name: FmOsc
defs.value: FmOsc { ctx, primary, gain, fm_gain, fm_osc, fm_freq_ratio, fm_gain_ratio }

defs.name: primary
defs.docs: The primary oscillator.  This will be the fundamental frequency

defs.name: fm_osc
defs.docs: The oscillator that will modulate the primary oscillator's frequency

defs.name: fm_freq_ratio
defs.docs: The ratio between the primary frequency and the fm_osc frequency.

defs.name: set_gain
defs.docs: Sets the gain for this oscillator, between 0.0 and 1.0.

defs.name: set_fm_amount
defs.docs: This should be between 0 and 1, though higher values are accepted.

defs.name: set_fm_frequency
defs.docs: This should be between 0 and 1, though higher values are accepted.
